description: Gets a generated file. When calling this method via REST, only the metadata of the generated file is returned. To retrieve the file content via REST, add alt=media as a query parameter.

schema.description: OAuth 2.0 token for the current user.

API key. Your API key identifies your project and provides you with
API access, quota, and reports. Required unless you provide an OAuth 2.0 token.
Required. The name of the generated file to retrieve. Example: `generatedFiles/abc-123`
